<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_129" id="64v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_129_r1l18"><expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Mayer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_129_r1l19">Hanns Mayr wır <expan>gepıet<ex>en</ex></expan> dır bey dem eyd . daʒ du niht laſſeſt du </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l20">komeſt auf <expan>mıtwoch<ex>en</ex></expan> nehſt . für rat für vns . wan wır mıt dır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l21">ʒureden haben . daran tuſt du <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex>ſıgıllo</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l22"><expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıcıuıu<ex>m</ex></expan> . <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan> Oculȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_129" id="64v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Mayer, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Hanns Mayr, wir <expan>gepiet<ex>en</ex></expan> dir bey dem eyd, daz du
                        niht lassest, du komest auf <app><note><q type="date"><expan>mitwoch<ex>en</ex></expan> nehst</q>06.03.1415</note></app> für rat
                        für uns, wan wir mit dir zu reden haben. Daran tust du
                                <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub </ex>sigillo</expan>
<expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan> oculi. </ab>
</div>
